rows.label: qst201410_msg0001
rows.name:
If we just keep drawing,
we're never going to be
able to determine a winner.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0002
rows.name:
Hey, Zakuro, Hikari! Have you two
been here chatting the whole time?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0003
rows.name:
Actually, we're trying to
work out which one of us
has the most Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah. Mikumari, could
you adjudicate for us?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0005
rows.name:
Hey, wait a sec... Are you
sure we should ask Mikumari?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0006
rows.name:
I mean, maybe we should ask
someone who's a bit more girly.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0008
rows.name:
Yes, perhaps she's not
the best candidate...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0009
rows.name:
If I'm being honest, she's
probably not up to the task...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0010
rows.name:
...Hey! You don't have to keep
going on and on about it, y'know!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0011
rows.name:
Anyway, if it's Girl Power
you're after, I'll have you
know I've got plenty!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0012
rows.name: More in fact!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0013
rows.name: Huh? No way!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0014
rows.name:
But you're so untidy, and always
losing things in your mess.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0015
rows.name:
And when you eat the food
goes everywhere! Ugh...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0016
rows.name:
You think Girl Power's all about waltzing
about like a little butterfly? No! It's
about being true to yourself!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0017
rows.name:
Don't you think that means you
don't have much Girl Power?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0018
rows.name:
Yeah, yeah! And I really think
you should stop leaping into
the bath like you always do.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0020
rows.name:
I tell you what, you two
can just figure out a
winner amongst yourselves.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0021
rows.name:
What a couple of jerks!
I have had enough!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0022
rows.name:
Erm... Maybe we did say
a bit too much there...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0023
rows.name:
Maybe we should take her
a little something later
to try and make it up.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0024
rows.name: Yeah, I think so.
